<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>WhatIfInlearing — Free Financial Education</title>
<meta name="description" content="Free financial education: calculators, market tools, credit guides, debt payoff strategies.">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
:root { --bg: #0a0a0f; --card: #16161f; --border: #2a2a35; --accent: #22c55e; --accent2: #3b82f6; --text: #f0f0f5; --muted: #8a8a95; }
body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.6; }
.hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 1rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #0a0a0f); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
.logo { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2)); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
.tagline { color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }
.container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; }
h2 { text-align: center; margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem; color: var(--accent); font-size: 1.5rem; }
.tools-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; }
.tool-card { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; transition: transform 0.2s; }
.tool-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); border-color: var(--accent); }
.tool-title { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.tool-desc { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.btn { display: block; padding: 0.7rem; background: var(--accent); color: var(--bg); text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; text-align: center; font-weight: 600; }
footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--muted); margin-top: 3rem; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header class="hero">
<div class="logo">WhatIfInlearing</div>
<div class="tagline">Free Financial Education — Tools, Calculators & Insights</div>
</header>
<div class="container">
<h2>💰 Financial Tools</h2>
<div class="tools-grid">
<div class="tool-card"><div class="tool-title">Tax-E-Software</div><div class="tool-desc">Tax calculation tools and guides</div><a class="btn" href="/tax-e-software">Open Tool</a></div>
<div class="tool-card"><div class="tool-title">Carbon Credit Exchange</div><div class="tool-desc">Simulated carbon credit trading</div><a class="btn" href="/carbon-credits">Open Tool</a></div>
<div class="tool-card"><div class="tool-title">LLM Cost Calculator</div><div class="tool-desc">Calculate AI API costs</div><a class="btn" href="/llm-cost-calc">Open Tool</a></div>
<div class="tool-card"><div class="tool-title">Freelance Calculator</div><div class="tool-desc">Rate calculator with expenses</div><a class="btn" href="/freelance-calc">Open Tool</a></div>
<div class="tool-card"><div class="tool-title">Salary Negotiator</div><div class="tool-desc">Remote salary comparison</div><a class="btn" href="/salary-negotiator">Open Tool</a></div>
<div class="tool-card"><div class="tool-title">Startup Cost Calculator</div><div class="tool-desc">Estimate startup launch costs</div><a class="btn" href="/startup-cost-calc">Open Tool</a></div>
</div>
</div>
<footer>
<p>WhatIfInlearing © 2025 | Not financial advice</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>